      offering to any third party, whether for a fee or free of charge.
  (c) Use the Software, in whole or in part, to generate revenue,
      reduce costs, or create commercial value, directly or indirectly.
  (d) Distribute, redistribute, sublicense, sell, lease, rent, or
      otherwise convey the Software (modified or unmodified) to any
      third party.
  (e) Remove, alter, obscure, or replace any copyright notice, license
      notice, branding, logo, or attribution in or on the Software.
  (f) Use the Pharos name, lighthouse logo, "A beam through the noise"
      tagline, or any associated trademarks for any purpose other than
      truthful, factual reference to this Software (no endorsement,
      derivative branding, or fork-renaming).
  (g) Train, fine-tune, or otherwise feed the Software (including its
      source code or any output it produces) into any machine-learning
      model intended for commercial use, redistribution, or any
      third-party access.
  (h) Use the Software in any safety-critical, life-critical, or
      regulated environment (including medical, automotive, aviation,
      nuclear, financial-trading, or government decisioning systems).


